		"description": "<blockquote><p>Your reliance on good fortune opens you up to new encounters and the benefits thereof.</p><p>Your reputation as a gambler precedes you, and there are members of any community you travel to that find your gambling ways to be a dangerous influence, particularly on the younger generations.</p></blockquote><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>Whenever you use the Gather Information downtime activity you can roll as many of your risk dice each week as you like.</p><ul><li><p>Even numbers on your dice reduce the gold cost by their value.</p></li><li><p>Odd numbers increase the gold cost by 1.</p></li></ul><p></p>",
